{"type": "article", "id": 57912, "title": "简洁实用的无线充电板，可同时为两部手机充电｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-11-01T23:32:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 53889, "name": "Nomad"}, {"id": 53890, "name": "N.HOOLYWOOD EXCHANGE SERVICE"}, {"id": 53891, "name": "HIPPOPOTAMUS"}, {"id": 53892, "name": "Christopher Farr"}, {"id": 53893, "name": "Anni Albers"}, {"id": 53894, "name": "Don Kwaning"}, {"id": 53895, "name": "Jean-Pascal Gauthier"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 94, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181102000717FNyruYvI6WfPt0Rs.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: #333333} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} span.s5 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s7 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s8 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Base Station by Nomad</h3><p>越来越多手机将无线充电功能纳入基础配置，不需要插线随手一放就能充电，的确颇为便利，可是当你想为智能手表、手机等多款产品同时充电时，是否要准备多个充电板呢？</p><p>最近，配件品牌 Nomad 推出一款名为 Base Station 的无线充电产品，不只满足你为手机充电的需求，还附有手表挂架。</p><p>Nomad Base Station 是铝合金搭配皮革的高质感底座，底座上附带有三个充电线圈，平板部分可以同时为两部手机充电，或是随意将手机放置在上面，就能开启充电功能。另外还配有一个有 MFi 认证的手表置放充电架，可以轻松为 Apple Watch 充电，漂亮且实用。售价 99.95 美元，<a href=\"https://hellonomad.com/products/base-station-hub\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181102000805DPBhKmzl2XZIQWRS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181102000805YNxolCgI1yqpLmvP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811020008055kP7BCGK2O0UDp1Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181102000804W5vD4kMI2eOZpTjd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181102000806wtA7RVQBFJmZOlEs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181102000810nCAx7OBtWRjMJ3v6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181102000825aAlIp9gr1K64MYPx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Big Pillow &amp; Cushion by  N.HOOLYWOOD EXCHANGE SERVICE &amp; HIPPOPOTAMUS</h3><p>日本设计品牌 N.HOOLYWOOD 旗下的 EXCHANGE SERVICE 支线，是以美军服饰为基础。最近，EXCHANGE SERVICE 与家居布艺品牌 HIPPOPOTAMUS 合作，为创立七周年的家居买手店 minka 设计了军事风格的 Big Pillow 和 Cushion 坐垫。</p><p>双方此前还合作推出过毛巾和浴巾，这次借助 HIPPOPOTAMUS 在布艺领域的生产经验，融入 EXCHANGE SERVICE 的军事风美学，同时采用优质有机棉以及竹纤维混纺而成，结合毛绒长度较短的设计，透着满满军事风格的同时，也减少了起毛球的可能性。</p><p>坐垫则交由日本枕具老字号品牌金泽屋的匠人负责制作，在棉料中加入人工纤维，提升其弹性。售价 14904 日元起，<a href=\"https://minka.thebase.in/items/14400028\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181102000901SRw0bk7pfGOm2or9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181102000901Zpt7YvOIqNcUgk9h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181102000902qk3TQe5hJHf9LVp1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181102000902BnPURViaI9ouSmvk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181102000902Ptb1xdKuEVSTe50w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181102000902OmBsoWb8gTJ1aFMQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Orchestra and Temple by Christopher Farr </h3><p>以纪念包豪斯先锋 Anni Albers 之名，英国纺织品牌 Christopher Farr 推出 Orchestra and Temple 系列地毯和面料新品。这个项目也是 Christopher Farr 和 Josef and Anni Albers 基金会持续合作的一部分。Anni Albers 是设计师，也是纺织艺术家，她在编织工艺领域的革新设计和先锋的创作理念为人所熟知，此外也涉及珠宝设计、版画等创作领域。</p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>新品部分灵感源自 Anni Albers 1920 年代造访过的柏林歌剧院。它由以看似随机的模式生成的四边形形状组成，令人联想到优雅的天鹅绒和蕾丝连衣裙。</p><p>在之前的 Anni Albers 面料系列中，Christopher Farr一直致力于小规模的单色图案。但新系列尝试了很多她的大型色彩作品的元素。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181102001010yLO1CiVK4Ym8NAJF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181102001029tIC8xkwfJbXnOzNR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181102001032uYGrfoWbDIZAFHwq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502961\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181102001305FenPt4a0sBYIX19m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811020013043E7Pnt8mVMbwqAGW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.336000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181102001308mh6XVGk9SsQpUqvj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181102001310zuVEon2TRJDfXY7B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181102001316BJvQu74l9wcnVTtO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://christopherfarr.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Christopher Farr</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Medulla by Don Kwaning</h3><p>埃因霍温设计学院的毕业生 Don Kwaning 创造了一种生态包装材料，取材自快速生长的植物灯心草。</p><p>这个项目名为 Medulla，Don Kwaning 希望能够拓展灯心草的新用途，尝试将木髓与纤维分开。Don Kwaning 的研究发现，这种纤维可以制作成纸、瓦楞纸板、绳索、无纺布和纺织品等材料。</p><p>轻质的木髓抗冲击和绝缘性能很好，适合用作生态包装材料。泡沫髓不需要任何粘合添加剂就能以不同的密度压缩，使其适合用作可用于家具生产的轻质片材。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181102001350pnHuDP59sIA03Q2Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181102001358e86wYMZQSJPuXiKC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181102001401QK2BgUJVfbIMkLyE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.387056\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018110200150168qVm1xRW7EQnYfa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.537225\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.donkwaning.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Don Kwaning</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Balancing Act of Color and Light by Jean-Pascal Gauthier</h3><p>蒙特利尔设计师 Jean-Pascal Gauthier 一直坚持自己的视觉风格，将无尽的形状和角度，纹理和材料，甚至生活结构融入其形式。Gauthier 在他的作品中擅于使用多样化的材料，诸如黄铜、不锈钢、大理石、花岗岩、镜子、玻璃、核桃木和丙烯酸的材料之间的平衡如何把握。</p><p>最近，Jean-Pascal Gauthier 在 2018 年米兰设计周的 Manfredi Style 当代设计展上亮相，其最新作品将透明玻璃材质和彩色圆形面板结合在一起，每个作品都是极简几何形式的再创作，试图演绎俄罗斯先锋派艺术家 El Lissitzky 的作品风格。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181102001526A2Y01nCBeRfwvpgV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.217593\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181102001526I5YH8pvaWGwkbBtV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181102001526IxKZp1niaOgt7EY4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.614062\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181102001527y16NaVO3QlkhrTpu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181102001527Wexn0fv351FIMdYp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181102001527YHj2tk3oE18CBW5L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/jean-pascal-gauthiers-balancing-act-color-light/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></p>"}